    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of any major wear or odors, with all electronic features and climate controls functioning as they should. It drives smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. This is a solid, honest car that offers a great balance of quality and value.",
