    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and stayed on top of every single service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for an adventure, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
