    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-caliber BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This naturally aspirated 3.2L straight-six is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering power through a variable M-differential lock. The vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS service and rod bearing replacement to ensure peak internal reciprocating health. The chassis is structurally perfect with a reinforced rear subframe, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. Every bushing, link, and damper remains tight, offering the visceral feedback and balanced handling characteristic of a true analog sports car. No paint corrections needed; the factory finish is flawless.",
      "price": 46500.0,
